---
// Hero section - IBC Academy homepage
---

<section class="relative py-16 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Light background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FAF9F6] via-[#F5F4F0] to-[#FAF9F6]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,_rgba(184,134,11,0.05)_0%,_transparent_50%)]"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left: Text content (first on mobile, first on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-1">
        <!-- Label -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-[#B8860B]"></span>
          <span class="label text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[#B8860B]">The Banking Function</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] leading-[1.1] mb-6 text-balance">
          <em class="text-[#B8860B] not-italic">34.5 cents</em> of every dollar goes to interest.
        </h1>

        <!-- Subheadline -->
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#4A4A4A] leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-xl">
          Not rate — volume. You're financing everything you buy, even when you pay cash. Nelson Nash spent 35 years teaching people how to flip that equation.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
          <a
            href="/learn/start-here"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 bg-[#B8860B] text-white font-bold text-base rounded-xl hover:bg-[#9A7209] transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-[#B8860B]/20"
          >
            Start Learning
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://calendar.app.google/H2wTUKcJnuhkpxFy8"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 bg-white border-2 border-[#E8E6E1] text-[#1A1A1A] font-semibold text-base rounded-xl hover:border-[#B8860B] hover:text-[#B8860B] transition-colors"
          >
            Book a Discovery Call
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Right: Brad's photo with quote (second on mobile, second on desktop) -->
      <div class="order-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative max-w-sm lg:max-w-md">
          <!-- Decorative element (top-left only, removed bottom-right to avoid quote overlap) -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-[#B8860B] rounded-lg opacity-20"></div>
          
          <!-- Photo container - portrait aspect ratio -->
          <div class="relative w-72 md:w-80 lg:w-96 aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img 
              src="/images/brad-raschke-hero.jpg" 
              alt="Brad Raschke - IBC Authorized Practitioner" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>
          
          <!-- Quote card - positioned below image, matches photo width -->
          <div class="mt-6 w-72 md:w-80 lg:w-96 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-4 border-l-4 border-[#B8860B]">
            <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A] italic font-serif">
              "I only teach one thing, and I teach it the way Nelson Nash intended."
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6B6B] mt-2 font-medium">— Brad Raschke</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
